data.description: This beautiful Ranch located on a Cul De Sac in the neighborhood offers everything you need! As you enter the home you are immediately greeted by the open floor plan, tons of natural light, large open foyer, and gourmet Kitchen ready for all of your entertaining needs! The kitchen overlooks the large living and dining space. There is a large fenced in backyard. This home offers 4 spacious bedrooms including the Master Suite with large master bathroom and walk in closet. New Carpet installed in all bedrooms and freshly painted interior !
